description: R U Cereal is the food truck love child of Breakfast and Dessert. A totally unique concept in the Mile High food truck scene - R U Cereal offers a cereal bar featuring over 20 of America's most loved cereals, as well as over 20 delicious toppings. Create your own, or choose one of our many R U Cereal creations - like 'Summer of George,' 'I Want S'More,' or 'Pray for Snow.' Then choose to pair your creation with milk, ice cream, a cupcake, yogurt, oatmeal, or a milkshake. We also offer local favorites like freshly brewed Pablo's Coffee®, Bonnie Brae Ice Cream®, Happy Leaf Kombucha® and much more. Let R U Cereal cater your next event, and we will bring the FUN!Peace, Love & Cereal.
name: R U Cereal
